<div id="pf11" class="pf w0 h28" data-page-no="11"><div class="pc pc11 w0 h28"><img class="bi x0 y0 w1 h29" alt="" src="bg11.png"/><div class="t m254 x8a h19 y24b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 2 July 6-12 </div><div class="t m255 x8b h2a y24c ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">e2TB [I:Ammo</div><div class="t m256 x8c h2a y24c ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-</div><div class="t m257 x8d h2a y24c ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12r </div><div class="t m258 x0 h2a y24d ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">arg.11Ek </div><div class="t m134 x23 h19 y24e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;I was born with nothing, and I will </div><div class="t m259 x52 h19 y24f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lie with nothing. The Lord gave, and </div><div class="t m25a x52 h19 y250 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">low he has taken away. May his name </div><div class="t m11f x52 h19 y9e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">)e praised!&quot; (Job 1:21, TEV). </div><div class="t m25b x23 h19 y251 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;When God sends us something </div><div class="t m25c x0 h19 y252 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">;ood, we welcome it. How can we </div><div class="t m217 x52 h19 y253 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">complain when he sends us trouble?&quot; </div><div class="t m232 x52 h19 y254 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job 2:10, TEV). </div><div class="t m25d x23 h17 y255 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">On the twenty-fourth day of </div><div class="t m1ea x0 h17 y256 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">December 1974 life was as usual in the </div><div class="t m25e x52 h17 y257 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Australian city of Darwin. People were </div><div class="t m25f x0 h17 ya7 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">doing their Christmas shopping, </div><div class="t m260 x0 h17 y258 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">wrapping gifts, preparing for loved </div><div class="t m261 x0 h17 y259 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ones, decorating their homes. </div><div class="t m262 x0 h17 y25a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Warnings came of an impending </div><div class="t m263 x0 h17 y25b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cyclone, but the citizens of the city had </div><div class="t m264 x0 h17 y25c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">seen high winds before and were not </div><div class="t m265 x0 h17 yad ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">greatly alarmed. Then the winds </div><div class="t m266 x0 h17 y25d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">struck-160 milesper hour in velocity. </div><div class="t m267 x0 h17 yb1 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ninety percent of the city was </div><div class="t m268 x0 h17 y25e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">destroyed. Thousands were </div><div class="t m269 x0 h17 y25f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">homeless. A reported 45 persons lost </div><div class="t m26a x0 h17 y260 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their lives, and many more were </div><div class="t m26b x0 h17 y261 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">injured. One television report showed </div><div class="t m26c x0 h17 y21a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">a man in a hospital bed. He and his </div><div class="t m26d x0 h17 y262 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">family had crouched in their yard </div><div class="t m26e x0 h17 y21c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">while their house was completely </div><div class="t m26f x0 h17 y263 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">destroyed. The wife and mother was </div><div class="t m270 x52 h17 y264 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">killed. For this family, disaster struck </div><div class="t m271 x52 h17 y265 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tragically all in a day. </div><div class="t m272 x77 h17 y266 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Since then more and perhaps </div><div class="t m273 x52 h17 y267 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">greater calamities have taken place in </div><div class="t m274 x52 h17 y268 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">this world. For millions of people </div><div class="t m275 x52 h17 y269 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disaster will strike—sometimes from  </div><div class="t m276 x57 h17 y26a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">natural causes, others because of </div><div class="t m277 x57 h17 y24f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sickness and accident, and perhaps </div><div class="t m278 x57 h17 y206 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">others—God forbid—because of war. </div><div class="t m26a x57 h17 y26b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">No doubt some who study these </div><div class="t m279 x57 h17 y26c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lessons will know how Job felt when </div><div class="t m27a x57 h17 y252 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">disaster struck for him. May God grant </div><div class="t m27b x57 h17 y253 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that Job&apos;s experience may help to </div><div class="t m27c x57 h17 y254 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rebuild broken lives. </div><div class="t m27d x8e h17 y26d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Job does not set out to answer the </div><div class="t m27e x8f h17 y255 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">problem of suffering, but instead </div><div class="t m27f x8f h17 y256 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shows that even a righteous man can </div><div class="t m280 x8f h17 y257 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">utilize such an experience as that </div><div class="t m281 x8f h17 y26e ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through which the hero passed to </div><div class="t m282 x57 h17 y26f ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">attain to new heights of emotional and </div><div class="t m283 x8f h17 y259 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual maturity. Quite obviously </div><div class="t m284 x8f h17 y25a ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nobody can be exempt from suffering, </div><div class="t m285 x8f h17 y25b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for where there are men there will </div><div class="t m26b x8f h17 y25c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">always be emotional and mental </div><div class="t m286 x8f h17 yad ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">conflicts, with corresponding adverse </div><div class="t m287 x8f h17 y270 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">effects. The supreme exemplar of the </div><div class="t m287 x8f h17 yb1 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">righteous sufferer was Jesus Christ, </div><div class="t m270 x8f h17 y271 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who neither explained nor dismissed </div><div class="t m288 x8f h17 y272 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">suffering, but instead absorbed it into </div><div class="t m289 x8f h17 y273 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His own spiritual experience, and </div><div class="t m28a x8f h17 y274 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through His fellowship with God </div><div class="t m28b x8f h17 y275 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">achieved what Rowley has happily </div><div class="t m28c x8f h17 y276 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">styled &apos;the wresting of profit from the </div><div class="t m28d x8f h17 y277 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">suffering,&apos; which has been of </div><div class="t m28e x8f h17 y278 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">incalculable value to subsequent </div><div class="t m28f x8f h17 y279 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">humanity.&quot;—R. K. Harrison, </div><div class="t m290 x8f h17 y27a ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Introduction to the Old Testament </div><div class="t m291 x90 h17 y27b ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Grand Rapids, Mich.: Wm. B. </div><div class="t m292 x8f h17 y27c ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Eerdmans Publishing Co., 1969), p. </div><div class="t m293 x8f h17 y27d ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1046. </div><div class="t m294 x90 h19 ybf ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m63 x90 h19 y27e ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m295 x91 h19 y27f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Before the Storm </div><div class="t m296 x91 h19 y280 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 1:2, 3) </div><div class="t m65 x90 h19 y281 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m297 x91 h19 y282 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Trouble Brewing </div><div class="t m298 x91 h19 y283 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 1:9-11) </div><div class="t m67 x90 h19 y284 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m299 x91 h19 y285 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Tragedy Strikes </div><div class="t m29a x91 h19 ycd ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 1:18, 19) </div><div class="t m69 x90 h19 y286 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t mb x91 h19 y287 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Initial Responses </div><div class="t m87 x91 h19 ycf ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 1:20-22) </div><div class="t m6b x90 h19 y288 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m29b x91 h19 y289 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Three &quot;Friends&quot; </div><div class="t m22a x92 h19 y28a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 2:11, 12) </div><div class="t m6d x93 h19 y28b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m295 x91 h19 y28c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A Light Grows Dim </div><div class="t m29c x92 h19 y28d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Job 3:2-7) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
